{"article_id":"xtr7oA49KLDsAMWx","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Lois Lerner , the Internal Revenue Service official under fire for her department ' s targeting of tea party groups , has retired effective Monday ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"according to the IRS .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"But that development does not end the scandal","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"that burst into the open last May ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"when Ms. Lerner revealed","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"that tea party groups were undergoing extra scrutiny in their applications for tax exemption .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"Lerner ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"who was director of the IRS ' s section on tax-exempt organizations ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"had been placed on paid administrative leave ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"and remains under subpoena by the House Oversight and Government Reform Committee ,","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"which is investigating the scandal .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"\" Lois Lerner ' s exit from the IRS does not alter the Oversight Committee ' s interest","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"in understanding why applicants for tax exempt status were targeted and inappropriately treated","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"because of their political beliefs , \"","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"Rep. Darrell Issa","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"( R )","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"of California , chairman of the committee , said in a statement .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"Sen. Orrin Hatch of Utah , the top Republican on the Senate Finance Committee , also signaled his continued interest in the IRS targeting scandal .","depth":4},{"id":18,"text":"\" Just because Lois Lerner is retiring from the IRS","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"does not mean the investigation is over , \"","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"Senator Hatch said in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"\" Far from it .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"In fact , there are many serious unanswered questions","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"that must be addressed","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"so we can get to the truth . \"","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"The brouhaha has been a political boon to conservatives ,","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"who had long suspected","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"they were being targeted by the government in an effort","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"to undermine their activities .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"The issue is likely to figure in efforts","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"to energize conservatives for the 2014 midterms .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"Republicans already control the House ,","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"but have a shot","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"at taking over the Senate .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"Lerner emerged early as a key figure in the targeting scandal .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"In fact , it was she who brought the practice to light in public on May 10 ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"when she responded to an audience question","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"- later revealed to be planted -","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"at a legal conference .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"She stated","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"that the targeting was \" absolutely incorrect , \" \" insensitive , \" and \" inappropriate , \"","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"and that \" the IRS would like to apologize for that . \"","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"At a congressional hearing on May 22 , Lerner said","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"she was proud of her government service ,","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"and had done nothing wrong .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Then she refused to testify ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"citing her constitutional right against self-incrimination .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Starting in 2010 ,","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"the IRS began subjecting groups with names","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"that contained conservative keywords , such as \" tea party \" and \" patriot , \"","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"to additional scrutiny in their requests for tax exemption ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"which delayed their applications .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"It was later revealed that some progressive groups , such as those","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"associated with the Occupy movement ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"had undergone similar targeting , but not nearly as many as the tea party groups .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"A report by the Treasury Department ' s inspector general for tax administration","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"( TIGTA )","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"released on May 14","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"found","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"that inappropriate criteria were used","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"to identify tax-exempt applications for review ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"and that Lerner herself had been briefed on the targeting in June 2011 .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Bloomberg News reported Monday","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"that an internal IRS board was going to propose starting the process","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"of firing Lerner ,","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"though it had not concluded","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"that she had acted with political bias or willful misconduct .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"The report also indicated","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"her pension would not have been different","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"had she been fired .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"In a statement Monday","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"confirming Lerner ' s retirement ,","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"the IRS sought to reassure the public","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"that the agency had reformed its procedures .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"\" The IRS is making important progress","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"on fixing the underlying management and organizational deficiencies in the EO","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"[ exempt organizations ]","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"area","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"identified by TIGTA , \"","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"the statement said .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"\" Our goal is to restore the public ' s faith and trust in the tax system . \"","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"you care about","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"The statement continued :","depth":5},{"id":87,"text":"\" We have sent nearly 400,000 pages of documents to Congress","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"and facilitated dozens of employee interviews .","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"We look forward to continuing to cooperate with Congress and other investigations . \"","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"Public faith in the IRS is especially critical","depth":5},{"id":91,"text":"as the Affordable Care Act","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"( ACA )","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"is about to go into effect .","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"It will be the IRS ' s responsibility to determine","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"whether individuals have health insurance ,","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"as mandated under the ACA .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":193,"left":121,"right":192,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":107,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":98,"right":106,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":98,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":101,"right":105,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":2,"right":100,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":3,"right":99,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":105,"left":103,"right":104,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":103,"left":102,"right":8,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":102,"left":6,"right":7,"relatio